<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I have always heard that high charisma made the charm last longer but I have not noticed it.  When I am not holding the crude stein my charm last forever (Erudite Enchanter) but when I put the stein in my hand and I get the addition 20plus charism, I swear the charm doesnt last as long.  Maybe I am crazy, maybe not?  Have you noticed anything like that at all?<p>

Omer, Enchanter of the 19th season</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
