<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">The creatures resist your charm based on your charisma, the higher it is the lower the chance it will break. As a DE Enchanter I love running around West commons at 13th lvl with a Derv Thug, Ghoul, or YK as a pet, Darkweed snakes are fun as well just be sure the Pet is at spell range, as far away as possible if you do not have a SoW, even if you don't Color Flux will save you.<p>

Ahzad of Innoruuks Brood<br>
Bristlebane</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
